  entitySprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fa5dfd096c6e61742a7b552d75de9656, type: 3}
  introduction:
  - Present as required.
  actionSpeakFeedback:
  - "I am\u2026 an autonomous being.\r"
  - "Created\u2026 created by\u2026 researchers."
  - "My body is\u2026 unstable\u2026"
  - "That is why I am fitted with these\u2026 supports."
  - "They gave them to me\u2026"
  - They will not give out. Not now.
  - "And if they do\u2026 there is a procedure to\u2026 restore me\u2026"
  - Plenty of failures on the road to success.
  - "I am always there\u2026 to try again\u2026"
  actionPokeFeedback:
  - This one is a confusing jumble of meat and metal, layers of different materials
    too overlapped to tell which part really came first. Tubes are going in and out
    of its form, and some connect straight into a small, plastic box. There is a
    screen showing numbers and graphs. It beeps rhythmically.
  sparedDialogue:
  - "Another success\u2026 they will be\u2026 pleased."
